    Nicholas Moreles            (The University of Texas at Austin)

but others contributing input and feedback include

    Robert van de Geijn         (The University of Texas at Austin)
    Field G. Van Zee            (The University of Texas at Austin)

Much of the documentation for BLASpy closely follows the format and
wording of "libflame: The Complete Reference" by Field G. Van Zee.
Many thanks for his permission to utilize his work as a guide.

BLASpy is currently maintained by

